@Lancecontreras<br>
Right now that is the way RibbonWindow fakes the Windows XP window chrome.  It's not perfect but because of the way RibbonWindow is coded there is no way to have windows xp render its chrome; causing ribbonwindow to do all of it.  The bevels and other details of XP Chrome are hard to duplicate in a vector form and our focus was on having a usable Ribbon and the clean up would happen in the comming version.<br>
There are bugs open for the look and feel and it will get some love.
